root: ^CAT: You know, I used to take for granted that I was the one who would be swatting the flies.

s: ^I can't blame them for wanting to take revenge.
^I think the zombugs are kind of cool, actually.

g-0: ^CAT: Those bichos repugnantes keep trying to eat me, of course you take their side.

s: ^You should be flattered they think you're so tasty.
^I have this feeling that at least some of the zombugs are intelligent,

c-2: ^CAT: I'd rather be alive and unbothered.
c-3: ^CAT: I don't like those things; they're not natural.

g-1: ^ I'll meet you up ahead, okay?
